1. Download VS Express 2010 and install
http://download.microsoft.com/download/5/C/1/5C156922-CA10-49D8-B7E7-9BF092C3B6EB/VS2010ExpressCHS.iso

2. Download Windows SDK 7.1 and install
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=8279

3.Run setenv.cmd in cmd, or modify param in this batch file

4.Run build.cmd in cmd.
